Future
======

Here are some  things planned for TransComm:

   * Completely rewritten in StormC (no more HiSoft Basic crap :-) )

   * new Client/Server system

   * extremely expanded ARexx port

   * new powerful config editor with a nice GUI

   * complete RIPscrip 1.x support

   * freely definable menu system

   * direct support for `UMS', the Universal Message System for the
     Amiga

   * completly usable installation and deinstallation via Installer

   * many things more ('configurability 'til you drop dead but still
     easy to adjust to your needs)


@EndNode

