On Your Own
===========

That's  it,  folks,  you're on your own now.  I hope that this document
did what  is it's purpose:  to give you aid and assistance and not to
leave you alone  and  confused  by  your problems.  I tried to make it
as logical and easy  to  understand as possible but still enabling you
to use TransAmiga's full  power.   As  Sami  was too busy working on
the docs, I volunteered to write  the  new  docs.   They  are  now
completely rewritten, put into new formats  and  I  hope you like them.
